g.title: j3866362525
g.text: You seem upset. Is it something I said?

g.title: j1294380934
g.text: Right. You never would have seen an animal on Deimos. Predasites are like infested dogs with big ears. You'd love them.

g.title: j782219780
g.text: Ah right. You wouldn't know. It's an animal on Deimos. Don't worry your pretty little head over it.

g.title: j605113444
g.text: I didn't love being called boring.

g.title: j4035199783
g.text: Oh. I really didn't mean anything by it.

g.title: j2019160236
g.text: big ears are always cute! u see predasites often? ^_^

g.title: j3391867555
g.text: Only one can live. You or your furry companion. You must choose.

g.title: j2889538981
g.text: Don't worry! I just chopped up a tasty meal for our furry companion.

g.title: j3607397280
g.text: Actually no. They're hard to get close to... and kinda violent.

g.title: j106030108
g.text: Yeah! I'm good at sneaking up on them.

g.title: j2551124226
g.text: I'm even better at in-person hugs.

g.title: j2920919604
g.text: Honest. I'm sorry I upset you.

g.title: j2902560182
g.text: You're not boring, Aoi. I just thought I was being clever.

g.title: j1626746208
g.text: If you were really boring, I wouldn't be talking to you.

g.title: j1228152445
g.text: pray tell, why do u need to get close to a wild animal on Deimos?

g.title: j293368578
g.text: aaand why are we sneaking up on wild animals exactly?

g.title: j2661083960
g.text: ah right u wouldn't know. don't worry ur great big head over it ;)

g.title: j32022235
g.text: It seems the jury's convinced by your defense

g.title: j2093345594
g.text: Conservation. I work to preserve Deimos wildlife.

g.title: j4234354393
g.text: wut do u think is the secret to a perfect hug? ^_^

g.title: j699239412
g.text: No way! I did all this work and now you want to steal the glory of serving the dish?

g.title: j1932867113
g.text: Of course! Why don't you go ahead and serve the dish?

g.title: j2425616273
g.text: and grants you a fresh start

g.title: j3690602958
g.text: is there like... an over-population problem?

g.title: j2385235577
g.text: That was a joke. I'm actually part of a program to conserve them.

g.title: j1650751018
g.text: oh! that is so incredibly lovely ^_^

g.title: j654668171
g.text: Oh, I see Aoi's emoticons are back. I think that's a good sign.

g.title: j4184438130
g.text: that might be my new fave fact about u

g.title: j1763224969
g.text: it was a thumbs up btw. that first emoticon.

g.title: j224176793
g.text: I bet we can make something yummy if we work together next time <RETRO_EMOJI_HEART>

g.title: j3194329244
g.text: I'm kidding! I actually conserve wildlife on Deimos.

g.title: j1918406810
g.text: aaah u got me! that's lovely ^_^

g.title: j1902201959
g.text: Just wait until you learn even more about me ;)

g.title: j178185296
g.text: Thanks for clearing that up. LOL.

g.title: j796027376
g.text: Ah. It all makes sense now.

g.title: j1915004196
g.text: I bet you're right. I'd like that :)

g.title: j2626301927
g.text: Not as happy as I am.

g.title: j3152689662
g.text: that must be cuz u made it with so much love ^_^

g.title: j3940967890
g.text: that's ok ^_^ u did ur best right? it's the thought that counts!

g.title: j1458666463
g.text: I'm glad ur not into hunting endangered animals <RETRO_EMOJI_HEART>

g.title: j2617073054
g.text: lol I look forward to it

g.title: j3374470518
g.text: don't worry, space cowboy. u can always count on me to share the wonders of the past ^_^

g.title: j2576054413
g.text: I'll leave u to it, chef!

g.title: j2849355937
g.text: my first emoticon was supposed to be a thumbs up btw ^_^

g.title: j2054740515
g.text: Oh. Thanks for clearing that up.

g.title: j502385893
g.text: Ah. It all makes sense now.

g.title: j1485748884
g.text: but I'm going to say it's a predasite from now on!

g.title: j2466832680
g.text: Lol. You do whatever you think is best.
